<?xml version="1.0"?><eml:eml xmlns:eml="eml://ecoinformatics.org/eml-2.0.1" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" packageId="ching.39.7" scope="system" system="knb" xsi:schemaLocation="eml://ecoinformatics.org/eml-2.0.1 eml.xsd"><dataset scope="document"><title>Effect of Shading on Leaf Longevity of 18 Hedge Plants</title><creator id="1164098609953" scope="document"><individualName><givenName>I-Ching</givenName><surName>Huang</surName></individualName><organizationName>Division of Forest Biology, COA Forestry Research Institute, Taipei, Taiwan, R.O.C.</organizationName><positionName>Associate Researcher</positionName><electronicMailAddress>ching@tfri.gov.tw</electronicMailAddress></creator><abstract><para>This study used leaf longevity as indicator to test shading tolerance of 18 hedge plants by an shading experiment, which included non-shading, 30% shading, 50% shading, 80% shading and 90% shading. Not only plant species but also shading rate had significant influence to average leaf longevity. In most of plants, leaf-longevity was significantly quadric correlated to shading rate. After change leaf-longevity to variation-of-leaf-longevity and arrange them by the order of variation-of-leaf-longevity, we found that the responses of shading on leaf-longevity could significantly show the shading tolerance of the plants. According to the order of variation-of-leaf-longevity and correlation between leaf-longevity and shading rate, the plants could divide into five groups. Group I. Non-shading tolerance, included Neolitsea parvigemma, Ilex triflora var. Kanehirai, Fraxinus formosana, Bougainvillea spp. and Aglaia formosana.  Group II. High shading tolerance, included Murraya paniculata, Ardisia squamulosa, Distylium racemosum and Diospyros kotoensis. Group III. Slight shading tolerance, included Pittosporum pentandrum, Lantana camara and Ilex rotunda. Group IV. Middle shading tolerance, included Pyracantha koidzumii, Taxus sumatrana and Ardisia elliptica. Group V. Non response, included Gelonium aequoreum, Scolopia oldhamii and Diospyros vaccinioides.</para></abstract><keywordSet><keyword>shading tolerance, Diospyros kotoensis Yamazaki, Gelonium aequoreum Hance, Pittosporum pentandrum (Blanco) Merr., Murraya paniculata (Linn) Jack, Diospyros vaccinioides Lindl., Ardisia squamulosa Presl., Pyracantha koidzumii (Hay.) Rehder, Bougainvillea spp., Lantana camara, Taxus sumatrana (Miq.) de Laub., Ardisia elliptica Thunb., Neolitsea parvigemma (Hay.) Kanehira et Sasaki, Fraxinus formosana Hay., Aglaia formosana (Hay.) Hay., Ilex rotunda Thunb., Distylium racemosum Sieb.&amp; Zucc., Scolopia oldhamii Hance, Ilex triflora Blume var. Kanehirai (Yam.) S. Y. Hu.</keyword></keywordSet><intellectualRights><para>使用資料前請與資料擁有者聯繫</para></intellectualRights><coverage scope="document"><geographicCoverage scope="document"><geographicDescription>Taipei test aera</geographicDescription><boundingCoordinates><westBoundingCoordinate>121.5</westBoundingCoordinate><eastBoundingCoordinate>121.5</eastBoundingCoordinate><northBoundingCoordinate>25.0</northBoundingCoordinate><southBoundingCoordinate>25.0</southBoundingCoordinate></boundingCoordinates></geographicCoverage><temporalCoverage scope="document"><rangeOfDates><beginDate><calendarDate>2001-01-01</calendarDate></beginDate><endDate><calendarDate>2006-02-28</calendarDate></endDate></rangeOfDates></temporalCoverage></coverage><contact scope="document"><references>1164098609953</references></contact><methods><methodStep><description><section><title>一材料與遮陰處理</title><para>本試驗共包含18種適用綠籬植物</para></section></description><instrumentation>試驗苗木除馬櫻丹、九重葛、紅豆杉外，均為2-3年生之實生苗，各樹種之試驗前主幹株高各為馬櫻丹 10.7cm、九重葛 6.6cm、蚊母樹 40.3cm、臺東火刺木22.8cm、鐵冬青 80.1cm、臺灣海桐 84.9cm、臺灣白蠟樹 59.8cm、春不老67.2cm、楓港柿44.6cm、蘭嶼樹杞45.6cm、紅豆杉 32.8cm、蘭嶼柿70.7cm、月橘60.3cm、小芽新木薑子57.8cm、金平氏冬青45.1cm、魯花樹96.6cm、白樹仔69.5cm、台灣樹蘭49.9cm。苗木均定植於7寸盆，以泥碳土比蛭石比陽明山土1:1:2為介質，試驗期每日澆水2次，每3個月施用好康1號(14-12-14)100天型緩效肥(8克/每盆)一次。試驗之遮陰處理是溫室外完全不遮陰(0% shading)、塑膠溫室本身一層塑膠布(30% shading)、塑膠布溫室加覆一層白網(50% shading)、二層白網(80% )及一層白網一層黑網(90% )，遮陰網均為厚德牌，白網密度為50%，黑網密度為70%，經光量計(玖廷牌E90 quantum sensor)實測距地面175cm高的光量，於六月分9-15時之平均光量分別為不遮陰1018.9μmole．m-2．s-1，遮陰30%為784.2μmole．m-2．s-1，遮陰50%為533.4μmole．m-2．s-1，遮陰80%為210.3μmole．m-2．s-1，遮陰90%為73.6μmole．m-2．s-1。試驗從90年1月起至95年2月止。</instrumentation></methodStep></methods><access authSystem="knb" order="denyFirst" scope="document"><allow><principal>public</principal><permission>read</permission></allow></access><dataTable id="1194857124812" scope="document"><entityName>Modified of the effect of shading on leaf longevity variation of 18 hedge plants.</entityName><physical id="1194857106781" scope="document"><objectName>Modified of the effect of shading on leaf longevity variation of 18 hedge plants.</objectName><size unit="byte">1175</size><dataFormat><textFormat><numHeaderLines>1</numHeaderLines><recordDelimiter>#x0A</recordDelimiter><attributeOrientation>column</attributeOrientation><simpleDelimited><fieldDelimiter>,</fieldDelimiter></simpleDelimited></textFormat></dataFormat><distribution scope="document"><online><url function="download">ecogrid://knb/ching.40.2</url></online></distribution></physical><attributeList><attribute id="1194857124828" scope="document"><attributeName>樹種(species)</attributeName><attributeLabel>species</attributeLabel><attributeDefinition>樹種名稱</attributeDefinition><measurementScale><nominal><nonNumericDomain><textDomain><definition>樹種名稱</definition></textDomain></nonNumericDomain></nominal></measurementScale></attribute><attribute id="1194857124843" scope="document"><attributeName>遮陰度(shading)0％</attributeName><attributeLabel>遮陰度(shading)0％</attributeLabel><attributeDefinition>遮陰度為0%的時候葉片壽命增減率</attributeDefinition><measurementScale><ratio><unit><standardUnit>dimensionless</standardUnit></unit><precision>0.01</precision><numericDomain><numberType>real</numberType></numericDomain></ratio></measurementScale></attribute><attribute id="1194857124859" scope="document"><attributeName>遮陰度(shading)3